{
  "info": {
    "name": "EasyVTC — Filtre vehicle_type (Chauffeurs disponibles)",
    "_postman_id": "easyvtc-vehicletype-filter",
    "description": "Tests du filtre vehicle_type sur GET /reservations/drivers/available.\n\n**Prérequis**\n- Seed en base : `npx tsx supabase/seeds/run_test_drivers.ts`\n- 8 chauffeurs de test insérés (6 éligibles, 2 exclus)\n\n**Ordre d'exécution**\n1. 🔐 Login admin → stocke `admin_token`\n2.  Cas nominaux (sans filtre, filtre standard/berline/van)\n3. ⚠️  Cas limites (type inexistant, sans auth)\n4. 🔍 Vérification des exclusions (offline + suspendu)\n\n**Données de test (seed)**\n- standard : Mamadou Diallo, Fatou Sow\n- berline  : Pierre Martin, Sophie Dubois\n- van      : Ahmed Traoré, Claire Bernard\n-  Luc Moreau   (standard, is_online=false)\n-  Nina Petit   (berline, status=suspended)",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    { "key": "base_url",    "value": "http://localhost:4000", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "admin_token", "value": "",                      "type": "string", "description": "Auto-rempli par le login admin" }
  ],
  "item": [

    {
      "name": "🔐 Authentification",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "POST /auth/login — Admin",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('Status 200', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));",
                  "pm.test('ok: true',   () => pm.expect(pm.response.json().ok).to.be.true);",
                  "pm.test('Token présent', () => {",
                  "  const token = pm.response.json().data?.access_token;",
                  "  pm.expect(token).to.be.a('string').and.not.empty;",
                  "  pm.collectionVariables.set('admin_token', token);",
                  "});"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"admin@test.com\",\n  \"password\": \"Test1234!\"\n}",
              "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } }
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/auth/login",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["auth", "login"]
            },
            "description": "Remplacer les credentials par ceux du compte admin réel. Le token est stocké dans `admin_token`."
          }
        }
      ]
    },

    {
      "name": " Cas nominaux",
      "item": [

        {
          "name": "GET /drivers/available — sans filtre (6 résultats)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "const json = pm.response.json();",
                  "const data = json.data;",
                  "",
                  "pm.test('Status 200',   () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));",
                  "pm.test('ok: true',     () => pm.expect(json.ok).to.be.true);",
                  "pm.test('data est un tableau', () => pm.expect(data).to.be.an('array'));",
                  "",
                  "pm.test('Au moins 6 chauffeurs éligibles (seed)', () => {",
                  "  pm.expect(data.length).to.be.at.least(6);",
                  "});",
                  "",
                  "pm.test('Luc Moreau (offline) absent', () => {",
                  "  const emails = data.map(d => d.user?.email);",
                  "  pm.expect(emails).to.not.include('driver.offline@test.easyvtc.com');",
                  "});",
                  "",
                  "pm.test('Nina Petit (suspendue) absente', () => {",
                  "  const emails = data.map(d => d.user?.email);",
                  "  pm.expect(emails).to.not.include('driver.suspended@test.easyvtc.com');",
                  "});",
                  "",
                  "pm.test('Tous les résultats sont active + is_online', () => {",
                  "  data.forEach(d => {",
                  "    pm.expect(d.status,    `driver ${d.id}`).to.equal('active');",
                  "    pm.expect(d.is_online, `driver ${d.id}`).to.be.true;",
                  "  });",
                  "});"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [{ "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{admin_token}}" }],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/reservations/drivers/available",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["reservations", "drivers", "available"]
            }
          }
        },

        {
          "name": "GET /drivers/available?vehicle_type=standard (2 résultats)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "const json = pm.response.json();",
                  "const data = json.data;",
                  "",
                  "pm.test('Status 200', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));",
                  "pm.test('ok: true',   () => pm.expect(json.ok).to.be.true);",
                  "",
                  "pm.test('Exactement 2 chauffeurs standard (seed)', () => {",
                  "  const seedEmails = [",
                  "    'driver.standard1@test.easyvtc.com',",
                  "    'driver.standard2@test.easyvtc.com'",
                  "  ];",
                  "  const returnedEmails = data.map(d => d.user?.email);",
                  "  const seedCount = returnedEmails.filter(e => seedEmails.includes(e)).length;",
                  "  pm.expect(seedCount).to.equal(2, 'Mamadou et Fatou doivent être présents');",
                  "});",
                  "",
                  "pm.test('Tous les résultats ont vehicle_type=standard', () => {",
                  "  data.forEach(d => {",
                  "    pm.expect(d.vehicle_type).to.equal('standard', `driver ${d.id}`);",
                  "  });",
                  "});",
                  "",
                  "pm.test('Luc Moreau (offline) absent', () => {",
                  "  pm.expect(data.map(d => d.user?.email)).to.not.include('driver.offline@test.easyvtc.com');",
                  "});",
                  "",
                  "pm.test('Aucun chauffeur berline ou van', () => {",
                  "  data.forEach(d => {",
                  "    pm.expect(['berline', 'van']).to.not.include(d.vehicle_type, `type inattendu pour ${d.id}`);",
                  "  });",
                  "});"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [{ "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{admin_token}}" }],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/reservations/drivers/available?vehicle_type=standard",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["reservations", "drivers", "available"],
              "query": [{ "key": "vehicle_type", "value": "standard" }]
            }
          }
        },

